<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فَأَراادَ أَنْ يَسْتَفِزَّهُمْ مِنَ الْأَرْضِ:</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span> أي يستخفه، قال الشماخ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يطيع سفيه القوم إذ يستفزه ... ويَعْصي حكيما شيّبته الهزاهز<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ص]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[الاستفصاص]</span>: استفصّه: أي استخرج ما عنده.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">ويقال:</span> ما استفصصت: أي ما قدرت على أخذ شيء.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[الاستفلال]</span>: استفلّ منه شيئا: أي أخذ منه قليلًا على عسر.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>... التفعُّل<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[ت]</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[التَّفَتُّت]</span>: التكسر.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[ك]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[التفكُّك]</span>: يقال: فلان يتفكك: إذا لم يتماسك من الحمق.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[التفلّل]</span>: تفلَّلت مضاربُ السيف:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أي تكسَّرت.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[ن]</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[التفنُّن]</span>: فنّنه فتفنّن: أي صار فُنونا.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">وتفنَّن في العلم:</span> أخذ في فنونه.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>... التفاعُل<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
